  <title translate="true">Adding a sampling form</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">Adding a sampling form</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Heading2"><text styleclass="Heading2" translate="true">Add a sampling form</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Follow the same steps to add a sampling form, taking care to use the correct date.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="FormInclusion.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"></image></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">On the form itself, the inclusion date is not editable. &#160;It is derived from the date used when the form was added. The blue color in the item text indicates that it is not editable. &#160;The same goes for the </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">SubjectId</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">, this is derived from the sequence number that this person received when he/she was added to the database).</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">The only editable field is the </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">ClinicalStudy</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> field, where you can select via keyboard or mouse the substudy that this patient will be part of.</text></para>
  </body>
